properties.script:
[
    {"type":"narrate", "data":[
	["There was once a...", ["/s/assets/narration/therewasoncea.mp3"]],
	["Oh, hello. I'm the storyteller.", ["/s/assets/narration/ohhello.mp3"]],
	["It's my job to document the lives of all of these people.", ["/s/assets/narration/itsmyjob.mp3"]],
	["So far, I've done <%sofar%>, and I'm really starting to forget things.", ["/s/assets/narration/sofar.mp3", "/s/assets/narration/zero.mp3", "/s/assets/narration/startingtoforgetthings.mp3"]],
	["Maybe you can help! It's really easy, watch", ["/s/assets/narration/maybeyoucanhelp.mp3"]],
	["Once upon a time, <%parent_name%> met <%partner_name%> and things were good.", ["/s/assets/narration/onceuponatime2.mp3", "<%parent_name%>", "/s/assets/narration/met.mp3", "<%partner_name%>", "/s/assets/narration/andthingsweregood.mp3"]],
	["After some time, they had a child whom they named <%name%>.", ["/s/assets/narration/aftersometime.mp3", "<%name%>"]],
	["This child was much like any other child, and spent its early life learning to control its body (using W A S and D).", ["/s/assets/narration/thischildwas.mp3"]]
]}
]

[
    {"type":"narrate", "data":[
	["<%name%> moved on to school, and they excelled in many subjects.", ["<%name%>", "/s/assets/narration/movedontoschool.mp3"]],
	["Like everyone at the school, <%name%> hated the uniforms.", ["/s/assets/narration/likeeveryone.mp3", "<%name%>", "/s/assets/narration/hatedtheuniforms.mp3"]]
]},
    {"type": "colour", "key": "uniform", "title": "School uniform colour", "instruction": "What colour was the school uniform?"},
    {"type":"narrate", "data":[
	["How uncool! And the tie...", ["/s/assets/narration/howuncool.mp3"]]]},
    {"type": "image", "key": "tie", "title": "School uniform tie", "instruction": "Draw the tie", "width": 9, "height": 16, "guide": "/s/assets/guides/tie-guide.png"},
    {"type": "insantiateLazyNPC", "tag": "school-friends"}
]
